data.description: Introducing a charming 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom home with a two-car garage in a sought-after master-planned community of Rodeo Palms. This residence boasts updated paint throughout, NEW roof, complemented by ceramic tile flooring that adds a touch of elegance to the living spaces. The high ceilings create an airy and spacious atmosphere, enhancing the overall appeal of the home. Convenience is key with easy access to major highways. Hwy 6 and Hwy 288, as well as county Rd 58 making commuting a breeze. The property is equipped with a water softener for added comfort and maintenance. AC has been maintained and has been equipped with UV lighting.  Enjoy outdoor living on the covered patio, perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing. This well-maintained home offers a perfect blend of modern updates, plenty of closets for storage, and practical features in a community designed for a comfortable and enjoyable lifestyle including a fishing lake, swimming pools, tennis court, and more.
